### Youyu - Search
### Run this file after changes to search or hot-keyword behavior.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN

### Public keyword search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=Advanced%20Math

###

### Public keyword search (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=Math&page=1&pageSize=5

###

### Public keyword search with category filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=Dorm&categoryId=3

###

### Public product type filter (digital)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?productType=digital

###

### Public combined filter: keyword + category + productType
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=Math&categoryId=1&productType=digital

###

### Public hot-search ranking
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/hot

###

### Public search suggestions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/suggest?q=adv&limit=5

###

### Public search suggestions (blank / noise input should return empty list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/suggest?q=!!!&limit=5

###

### Admin: list search governance rules
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules
Authorization: Bearer mock-9001-ADMIN

###

### Admin: create a sensitive-word rule
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules
Authorization: Bearer mock-9001-ADMIN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ruleType": "SENSITIVE_WORD",
  "keyword": "counterfeit"
}

###

### Admin: create a hide-keyword rule
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules
Authorization: Bearer mock-9001-ADMIN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ruleType": "HIDE_KEYWORD",
  "keyword": "test"
}

###

### Admin: create a pin-keyword rule
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules
Authorization: Bearer mock-9001-ADMIN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ruleType": "PIN_KEYWORD",
  "keyword": "advanced math"
}

###

### Admin: update governance rule (toggle active)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules/1
Authorization: Bearer mock-9001-ADMIN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Admin: delete governance rule
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/governance-rules/1
Authorization: Bearer mock-9001-ADMIN

###

### Admin: browse search logs (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/search/logs?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer mock-9001-ADMIN

###

### Manual validation flow: create logs then verify governed suggestions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?keyword=Advanced%20Math

###

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search/suggest?q=adv&limit=5
